{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a7e397065a","title":"毛泽东对薄一波关于一九五三年国家预算报告稿的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e1e3e01843","index":0,"year":1953,"month":2,"day":9,"articleId":"a7e397065a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2e5956d88a","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对薄一波关于一九五三年国家预算报告稿的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"619d4eb997","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"47094f0e0e","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"5ccaf034f9","type":"paragraph","text":"表和报告印发给明天到会各人，请他们带回去研究，提出修改意见，写在便条上，于十一日带来。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"0f4d31f7ab","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"4635c50826","type":"appellation","text":"胡乔木同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"d7c9b0fc79","type":"paragraph","text":"请与齐燕铭联系，看是否有修改意见，收集起来，于明日（十四日）加以修改，送我一阅，准备于十五或十六日发表。请通知人民日报写一社论。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"b8df6a2319","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月十三日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"1e55f022fd","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"daa6ed485e","type":"paragraph","text":"这个新阶段是以过去三年恢复阶段中所获成绩为基础的。过去三年我们国家和人民的艰苦奋斗和一致团结，使得我们解决了恢复经济这个严重的问题。我们的国家已比国家初建时的那种残破不全的情况完全不同了，我们的经济一般已经恢复到过去最高年产量的水平，其中大多数项目则已超过了这一水平，有些并已超过得很大。这样就给了我们以开始进行第一个五年经济建设计划的可能，就给第一个五年计划奠定了基础。一九五三年是第一个五年经济建设计划的第一年。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"83dee00ee5","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"237fe45c8a","type":"paragraph","text":"个人所得税是一切财政制度上了轨道的国家都实行的，这不但是为了国家的收入，而且是为了养成国民对于国家事业的关心的一种物质的表现。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"74bc741505","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"},{"id":"bb4b4afaa5","type":"paragraph","text":"公债一方面是人民的储蓄，一方面又是人民对国家关心的一种表现，它是爱国主义的。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a"}],"page":{"id":"aad29c143a","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a7e397065a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}